net.pandoragames.far.ui.model

Class OperationForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.pandoragames.far.ui.model.OperationForm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, Resetable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FARForm, RenameForm

    public abstract class OperationForm
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, Resetable
    Common base class for FAR data models. Each tab of the FAR GUI is backed by a specialized form class. The form receives data from the UI and serves as "protocol" for the backend.
    Author:
    Olivier Wehner
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
